《'''透过窥镜'''》（{{lang-en|Through the Looking Glass}}）是[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]电视剧《[[迷失|迷失]]》[[迷失_(第三季)|第3季]]的第22和23集，也是全剧的第71集和72集，由[[执行制作人|执行制作人]][[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]和卡尔顿·库斯[[编剧|编剧]]，林道夫还是节目统筹之一，[[导演|导演]]则是另一名执行制作人[[杰克·本德|杰克·本德]]。节目于2007年5月23日在[[美国电视|美国]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]][[首演|首播]]，共计吸引了1400万美国观众收看。与之前两季的[[季终集|季终集]]一样，本集加上插播广告一共也持续有两个小时，比往常的剧集长一倍，到之后发行{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}时又剪成上下集两部分。部分评论认为，《透过窥镜》是《迷失》中最优秀的剧集，节目还获得多个奖项提名，其中包括3项[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]提名和1项[[美国导演工会奖|美国导演工会奖]]提名。

这集的剧情从2004年12月下旬开始，距[[海洋航空|海洋航空]]815号航班坠毁已经过了90余天。航班幸存者和此前就住在岛上，表现得既神秘又危险的“[[迷失角色列表|其他人]]”之间的斗争已进入白热化。10个其他人发起偷袭，但悉数被杀。与此同时，[[杰克·谢泼德|杰克·谢泼德]]（[[马修·福克斯|马修·福克斯]]饰）率领大部分幸存者朝岛上的无线电发射塔进发，希望能同距岛不远的一艘货船取得联系。剧集中插入闪回剧情，杰克变得非常沮丧，而且重度酗酒，还对止痛药上瘾，并且一度打算自杀。结局的[[大逆转|大逆转]]表明这段剧情并不像之前的《迷失》中那样都属于回忆，而是讲述杰克离开坠机岛屿之后发生的事情。

== 剧情 ==
“[[迷失角色列表|其他人]]”计划袭击[[海洋航空|海洋航空]]815号航班幸存者的营地，把任何怀孕的妇女都绑架回来用于科学研究<ref name="AUTOREF2">{{cite episode | credits = Kelley, Dawn Lambertsen (writer) & Ragghianti, Matt (writer) & [[杰克·本德|Bender, Jack]] (director). | title = Maternity Leave | series = ''[[迷失|Lost]]'' | network = [[美国广播公司|ABC]] | number = [[迷失剧集列表|15]] | season = [[迷失_(第二季)|2]] | airedate = 2006-03-01}}</ref>。但本的养女[[艾莉克斯·卢梭|艾莉克斯]]（坦妮娅·雷蒙德饰）说服男友[[迷失角色列表|卡尔]]（布莱克·巴绍夫饰）前去海滩警告幸存者，幸存者的领袖[[杰克·谢泼德|杰克·谢泼德]]（[[马修·福克斯|马修·福克斯]]饰）计划用炸药杀死前来偷袭的人<ref name="hits">{{cite episode | credits = Kitsis, Edward (writer) & Horowitz, Adam (writer) & Williams, Stephen (director) | title = [[精选辑_(迷失)|Greatest Hits]] | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 21 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-05-16}}</ref>。[[萨伊德·贾拉|萨伊德·贾拉]]（[[纳威恩·安德利维斯|纳威恩·安德利维斯]]饰）、[[权真秀|权真秀]]（[[金大贤|金大贤]]饰）和[[柏纳·纳德勒|柏纳·纳德勒]]（山姆·安德森饰）留在营地，等“其他人”来袭时再引爆炸药，其他幸存者则跟随[[达妮艾尔·卢梭|达妮艾尔·卢梭]]（米拉·福兰饰）前往无线电发射塔，试图与纳奥米·杜丽位于近海的货船取得联系。其他人来袭时，萨伊德和柏纳都引爆了炸药，炸死7个来袭者，但权真秀却没有打中目标，以致3人都被汤姆（迈克·康纳·盖尼饰）、瑞安·普赖斯（布莱恩·古德曼饰）和杰森（阿里斯顿·格林饰）所擒<ref name="AUTOREF3">{{cite video | title = "The World of the Others", in ''Lost: The Complete Third Season – The Unexplored Experience'' | publisher = Buena Vista Home Entertainment | date = 2007-12-11 | medium = DVD Featurette, disc 7}}</ref>。由于只听到两响爆炸声，[[詹姆斯·「索耶」·福特|詹姆斯·「索耶」·福特]]（[[乔什·哈洛威|乔什·哈洛威]]饰）和[[茱莉叶·柏克|茱莉叶·柏克]]（[[伊丽莎白·米切尔|伊丽莎白·米切尔]]饰）转身赶回营地，去看看到底发生了什么事，自己能否帮上忙。[[休戈·「赫利」·瑞斯|休戈·「赫利」·瑞斯]]（[[乔治·加西亚|乔治·加西亚]]饰）也想一起前往，但索耶和朱莉叶不同意，觉得体型过胖的休戈只会帮倒忙。结果休戈开着他在海滩上找到的面包车<ref name="AUTOREF4">{{cite episode | credits = Kitsis, Edward (writer) & Horowitz, Adam (writer) & Laneuville, Eric (director) | title = Tricia Tanaka is Dead | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 10 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-02-28}}</ref>，在冲突中靠着索耶和朱莉叶的帮助取得上风，杀死了另外两个其他人<ref name="two">{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Through the Looking Glass | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 23 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-05-23}}</ref>，汤姆虽然投降，但还是被索耶枪杀。

[[查理·佩斯|查理·佩斯]]（[[多米尼克·莫纳汉|多米尼克·莫纳汉]]饰）潜入[[达摩计划|达摩计划]]水下工作站“窥镜”后被常驻该站的其他人葛丽泰（拉娜·帕瑞娅饰）和邦妮（特雷西·米登道夫饰）所擒。[[本杰明·莱纳斯|本杰明·莱纳斯]]（[[迈克尔·爱默生|迈克尔·爱默生]]饰）得知此事后命令米哈伊尔·巴枯宁（安德鲁·迪沃夫饰）前去将3人全部杀死，防止窥镜的信息干扰功能失效。米哈伊尔进入工作站后杀害了葛丽泰和邦妮，但很快就被藏身壁橱内的[[德斯蒙德·休谟|德斯蒙德·休谟]]（[[亨利·伊安·库斯克|亨利·伊安·库斯克]]饰）用鱼枪射中胸口而倒下。原来他在上集中虽被好意的查理打晕<ref name="hits" />，但很快就苏醒过来，并且在查理进入后不久也潜入窥镜躲了起来。邦妮临死前吐露了机关的操作密码（[[海滩男孩|海滩男孩]]歌曲《{{lang|en|[[Good_Vibrations|Good Vibrations]]}}》中间的8段音符），查理关闭了干扰信号，然后收到德斯蒙德女友潘妮·威德摩尔（索尼亚·瓦格尔饰）发来的视频信号。潘妮告诉查理，她从来没听说过哪个叫纳奥米的人，也没有像纳奥米声称的那样派出船只找寻德斯蒙德。米哈伊尔虽然身受重伤，但却成功逃出工作站，然后在水中引爆手榴弹，炸死自己的同时，也炸破了工作站通讯室的玻璃。<ref name="AUTOREF5">{{cite interview | subject = [[戴蒙·林道夫|Lindelof, Damon]] & Cuse, Carlton | date = 2007-09-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090811055443/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast#t=3421 | archivedate = 2009-08-11 | url = http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast#t=3421 | program = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | callsign = ''ABC'' | accessdate = 2009-08-11}}{{dead link|date=March 2016}}</ref>海水立即涌入通讯室，为避免德斯蒙德也被淹死，查理锁住了通讯室的门，并且临死前在自己手上写下文字告诉德斯蒙德，那艘船根本不是潘妮派来的<ref name="two" />。

幸存者[[约翰·洛克_(迷失)|约翰·洛克]]（[[特瑞·欧奎恩|特瑞·欧奎恩]]饰）被本用枪打中<ref name="AUTOREF6">{{cite episode | credits = Goddard, Drew (writer) & Sarnoff, Elizabeth (writer) & Roth, Bobby (director). | title = The Man Behind the Curtain | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 20 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-05-09}}</ref>，苏醒过来后发现双腿又像飞机失事前那样失去了知觉，下半身瘫痪，他打算[[自杀|自杀]]，但[[沃特·劳伊德|沃特·劳伊德]]（马尔科姆·大卫·凯利饰）却突然出现阻止了他。与此同时，本要求理查德·阿尔珀特（内斯特·卡博内尔饰）带领剩下的其他人前往“神庙”，他则带养女艾莉克斯（[[达妮艾尔·卢梭|达妮艾尔·卢梭]]的亲生女儿<ref name="AUTOREF7">{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = I Do | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 6 | season = 3 | airedate = 2006-11-08}}</ref>）主动去找幸存者，希望能说服杰克不要联络纳奥米的船只求救<ref name="one">{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Through the Looking Glass | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 22 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-05-23}}</ref>。

索耶之前返回营地帮助萨伊德等人时不愿[[凯特·奥斯顿|凯特·奥斯顿]]（[[伊万杰琳·莉莉|伊万杰琳·莉莉]]饰）同去，这让凯特很难过。杰克于是安慰她，索耶只是想保护她。凯特反问杰克，为什么要给索耶辩护，杰克回答，因为索耶爱她。本和艾莉克斯追上杰克等人，本告诉杰克，纳奥米隐瞒了自己的真实身份，同她联系将给岛上所有人带来灾难性的后果。本命令手下枪杀萨伊德、权真秀和柏纳，杰克听到3声枪响后突然冲上去痛打本，一拳又一拳地打在对方脸上，打得本满脸都是血。但杰克并没想到，本的手下只是遵归本此前的命令对着沙滩开枪，并没有真的杀死萨伊德等人。卢梭终于和已经16岁大的女儿艾莉克斯重聚，当年她刚出生就被其他人绑架。<ref name="AUTOREF8">{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Exodus | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 23 | season = 1 | airedate = 2005-05-16}}</ref>众人将本绑起来，经过长途跋涉，大家终于来到无线电放射塔有效范围内，电话有了信号。卢梭关闭了求救信号，调整频率以便同纳奥米通讯。但是，纳奥米已经被洛克从背后用刀所杀，他还威胁要是杰克联系纳奥米的船，就连杰克也要杀掉。杰克与纳奥米船上的乔治·明可夫斯基（[[费舍·史蒂芬斯|费舍·史蒂芬斯]]饰）取得联系，后者告诉幸存者，船上会派人前去救援。<ref name="two" />

本集的闪回镜头是围绕杰克展开，他看起来很失落，满脸胡须，重度酗酒，而且对[[羟考酮|羟考酮]]成瘾。得知自己认识的某人去世后，杰克打算从[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的[[第6大街高架桥|第6大街高架桥]]跳下去[[自杀|自杀]]。但就在这时发生了一起车祸，他马上前去救治伤者。之后，杰克前去参加自己认识的那个人的追悼会，但却只有他一人到场。最后，凯特前来和杰克交谈，两人谈起之前815航班坠毁的那个岛，原来这段闪回镜头的内容并不是发生在过去，而是将来。<ref name="AUTOREF9">{{cite web|last=Snierson |first=Dan |date=2008-01-04 |title=''Lost''s Matthew Fox Flashforwards to Season 4 |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-11-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129032342/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20169281_2%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20169281_2,00.html |archivedate=2014-11-29 }}</ref>杰克告诉凯特追悼会上的事，凯特表示自己不知情，但即使知道也不会参加。杰克还表示，他每周五都会用[[海洋航空|海洋航空]]送给每位815航班幸存者的金卡搭飞机穿越[[太平洋|太平洋]]，期望会再度坠机，落到那个岛上。他悲伤地感叹，他们根本就不应该离开那座岛，必须要回去。但凯特并不同意并起身离开，显然两人之前也讨论过这个问题。<ref name="AUTOREF10">{{cite web | author1 = Lindelof, Damon | author2 = Cuse, Carlton | date = 2007-07 | title = Black Box: Oceanic Flight 815 Recorder | work = Lost: The Official Magazine | accessdate = 2012-11-12 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-11-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121112144646/http://bp1.blogger.com/_RrObyQ3XzcY/RrXf2cJdKeI/AAAAAAAAHZU/44tL9iXE5WY/s1600-h/BlackBox3.jpg | url = http://bp1.blogger.com/_RrObyQ3XzcY/RrXf2cJdKeI/AAAAAAAAHZU/44tL9iXE5WY/s1600-h/BlackBox3.jpg}}</ref>

== 制作 ==
[[File:Lost_chair.jpg|right]]，执行制作人[[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]、卡尔顿·库斯和[[布赖恩·伯克|布赖恩·伯克]]。]]

本集标题意指[[路易斯·卡罗|路易斯·卡罗]]的小说《[[爱丽丝镜中奇遇|爱丽丝镜中奇遇]]》<ref name="podcast">{{cite web | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ''ABC'' | date = 2007-05-21 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070521.mp3 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185808/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070521.mp3 | deadurl = yes | format = MP3}}</ref>，根据[[精选辑_(迷失)|上集]]剧情，窥镜是指[[达摩计划|达摩计划]]的水下工作站<ref name="hits" />。节目于2007年4月13日开拍<ref name="AUTOREF11">{{cite web | last = Perez | first = Mario | date = 2007-05-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100206170431/http://abcmedianet.com/web/display/display_main.aspx?global_id=001648&leftcol=links | url = http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/display/display_main.aspx?global_id=001648&leftcol=links | title = ''Lost'' Photography | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | accessdate = 2010-02-06 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2010-02-06}}</ref>，同年5月7日完成<ref name="AUTOREF12">{{cite web | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | date = 2007-05-11 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070511.mp3 | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ''ABC'' | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | format = MP3 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185826/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070511.mp3}}</ref>。众编剧的工作进度严重滞后，以致本集开拍后，还有部分剧情尚未创作完成<ref name="AUTOREF13">{{cite video | people = Cuse, Carlton & [[伊万杰琳·莉莉|Lilly, Evangeline]] & Holloway, Josh | title = "I Do" in ''Lost: The Complete Third Season – The Unexplored Experience'' | publisher = Buena Vista Home Entertainment | chapter = Audio commentary, disc 2 | date = 2007-12-11}}</ref>。拍摄工作主要是在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]的[[欧胡岛|欧胡岛]]进行，还有部分镜头在洛杉矶取景<ref name="AUTOREF14">{{cite web | url = http://www.lostvirtualtour.com/lost/episode/3x22.html | title = Episode 3x22&23: 'Through the Looking Glass' – Parts 1 & 2 Hawaii | work = ''Lost Virtual Tour'' | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402152429/http://www.lostvirtualtour.com/lost/episode/3x22.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2015-04-02 }}</ref>。用于拍摄本集医院镜头的外景地也是美国广播公司另一部电视剧《[[实习医生格蕾|实习医生格蕾]]》的外景地<ref name="AUTOREF15">{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon | date = 2007-07-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402115415/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-in-los-angeles-7918.aspx | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-in-los-angeles-7918.aspx | title = ''Lost'' in Los Angeles? | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-03 | archivedate = 2015年4月2日 }}</ref>。

已经15岁的马尔科姆·大卫·凯利（{{lang|en|Malcolm David Kelley}}）回归出演10岁大的[[沃特·劳伊德|沃特·劳伊德]]一角<ref name="AUTOREF16">{{cite episode | credits = [[J·J·艾布斯|Abrams, J.J.]] (writer/director) & Lindelof, Damon (writer) & [[杰弗瑞·利柏|Lieber, Jeffrey]] (writer) | title = [[试播_(迷失)|Pilot]] | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 2 | season = 1 | airedate = 2004-09-29}}</ref>，不过美国广播公司事先发布的正式新闻稿中没有透露这一消息<ref name="press">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2007-05-07 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050707_12 | archivedate = 2014-08-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140815061042/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050707_12 | title = ''Lost'' Season Finale Entertainment Press Release | accessdate = 2014-08-15 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，凯利之后在演职人员名单属于“特别客串明星”<ref name="AUTOREF17">{{cite web | work = Entertainment Yahoo! TV Beta | accessdate = 2012-03-20 | url = http://tv.yahoo.com/malcolm-david-kelley/contributor/575325 | title = Malcolm Kelley | publisher = ''Yahoo!'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120320025546/http://tv.yahoo.com/malcolm-david-kelley/contributor/575325 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-03-20}}</ref>。这是凯利自第2季结束后首次在《迷失》中亮相<ref name="AUTOREF18">{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Live Together, Die Alone | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 24 | season = 2 | airedate = 2007-05-24}}</ref>，如果按剧情中的时间计算，他上一次出现是在《透过窥镜》的故事发生26天前，但凯利实际上已经有1年多没有参与本剧演出。沃尔特在本集中的出场镜头只有1个，他看上去明显大了一些，身材更高，而且嗓音也更加低沉<ref name="AUTOREF19">{{cite web | work = ''BuddyTV'' | title = ''Lost'' Season Three Finale - Favorite Moments! | date = 2007-05-25 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/more/lost-season-three-finale-favor-6943.aspx | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150415155941/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/more/lost-season-three-finale-favor-6943.aspx | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | archivedate = 2015-04-15 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。节目的[[制作人|制作人]]本期望扮演沃尔特父亲[[麦可·道森_(Lost档案)|麦克·道森]]的[[哈罗德·佩里诺|哈罗德·佩里诺]]（{{lang|en|Harold Perrineau}}）也能参加本集演出，但他这时正忙于拍摄[[CBS_(电视网)|哥伦比亚广播公司]]电视剧《群魔》（{{lang|en|Demons}}）的[[电视试播|试播集]]<ref name="AUTOREF20">{{cite web|last=Bruno |first=Mike |date=2007-08-06 |accessdate=2014-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819155422/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20050265%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-08-19 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20050265,00.html |title=''Lost'': The Return of Michael Dawson |deadurl=yes |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' }}</ref>。此外，[[执行制作人|执行制作人]][[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]和卡尔顿·库斯（{{lang|en|Carlton Cuse}}）分别在剧中为没有露面的机长和新闻主播[[配音|配音]]<ref name="AUTOREF23">{{cite web | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | date = 2007-05-04 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070504.mp3 | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ''ABC'' | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | format = MP3 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185921/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070504.mp3 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

