多米尼克·莫纳汉饰演的查理·佩斯一角会在这集中死亡，这一故事主线从第3季早期就已展开，能够准确预料他人未来的德斯蒙德·休谟预言查理将会去世<ref name="AUTOREF24">{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Goddard, Drew (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Flashes Before Your Eyes | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 8 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-02-14}}</ref>。查理在第3季里曾死里逃生<ref name="AUTOREF25">{{cite episode | credits = Kim, Christina M. (writer) & Rosenberg, Jordan (writer) & Edwards, Paul (director) | title = Par Avion | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 12 | season = 3 | airedate = 2007-03-14}}</ref>，但德斯蒙德告诉他，只有在查理死后，女友[[克莱尔·李特顿|克莱尔·李特顿]]（[[艾蜜莉·迪瑞文|艾蜜莉·迪瑞文]]饰）和孩子亚伦才会获救离开这个岛<ref name="hits" />。查理之前的[[海洛因|毒瘾]]剧情主线在[[迷失_(第二季)|第2季]]末结束<ref name="AUTOREF27">{{cite episode | credits = Kitsis, Edward (writer) & Adam Horowitz (writer) & Williams, Stephen (director) | title = Three Minutes | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 22 | season = 2 | airedate = 2006-05-17}}</ref>，然后编剧就开始设计让他死亡的剧情<ref name="AUTOREF26">{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-05-23 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-exec-on-8445/ | title = Ausiello Report – Lost Exec on Last Night's Big Death: "It Was Painful" | publisher = ''TV Guide'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070707215534/http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Ausiello-Report/Lost-Exec-Nights/800015786?start=225& | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | archivedate = 2007-07-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。莫纳汉是在拍摄第3季第20集《幕后高人》（{{lang|en|''The Man Behind the Curtain''}}）时得知自己角色的命运<ref name="AUTOREF28">{{cite web|last=Snierson |first=Dan |date=2007-05-24 |accessdate=2014-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819154529/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20040051_2%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20040051_2,00.html |title=The Q&A: Sorry, Charlie (Part 2) |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |archivedate=2014-08-19 }}</ref>，对此感觉“松了口气”<ref name="AUTOREF29">{{cite news | last = Snierson | first = Dan | date = 2007-05-18 | archivedate = 2015-04-11 | title = Spotlight on Dominic Monaghan | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411001248/http://www.ew.com/article/2007/05/18/spotlight-dominic-monaghan | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2007/05/18/spotlight-dominic-monaghan | work = ''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-02}}</ref>。莫纳汉在外景地参加演出的倒数第2个晚上，剧组和众演员送给他一根自制的独木舟桨<ref name="AUTOREF30">Snierson, Dan, (May 24, 2007) "[http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20040051,00.html The Q&A: Sorry, Charlie (Part 1)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20040051,00.html |date=20070702195208 }}", ''Entertainment Weekly''.  Retrieved on July 7, 2007.</ref>。不过，莫纳汉在接受采访时表示，还是希望今后能够以客串形式在节目的闪回镜头或梦境中出现<ref name="AUTOREF31">{{cite web | last = Malcolm | first = Shawna | date = 2007-05-24 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/sorry-charlie-lost-35854.aspx | title = Sorry, Charlie: ''Lost'' Star Wanted to "Die" a Hero | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2014-11-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141104215807/http://www.tvguide.com/news/sorry-charlie-lost-35854.aspx | archivedate = 2014-11-04 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

据杰克·本德表示，马修·福克斯“真的是全身心投入到他所讲述的故事中”，福克斯则感觉参与两集长度节目的演出工作量实在很大，自己从来没觉得这么累过<ref name="AUTOREF32">{{cite video | title = "Lost: On Location – Through the Looking Glass" in ''Lost: The Complete Third Season – The Unexplored Experience'' | publisher = Buena Vista Home Entertainment | medium = DVD Featurette, disc 7 | date = 2007-12-11}}</ref>。与前两季《迷失》的季终集一样，《透过窥镜》最后的悬念镜头也有代号——“邮箱里的响尾蛇”（{{lang|en|The Rattlesnake in the Mailbox}}）——并保持绝密<ref name="AUTOREF33">{{cite web|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819160220/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20036782_20037403_20038202_3%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20036782_20037403_20038202_3,00.html |title=A Map for ''Lost'' |deadurl=yes |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-08-19 |archivedate=2014-08-19 }}</ref>。林道夫和库斯写完这场戏的剧本后，只有福克斯、莉莉、本德和执行制作人让·希金斯（{{lang|en|Jean Higgins}}）有拿到剧本副本。这场戏是采用[[色键|绿幕]]技术在[[檀香山|檀香山]]某废弃停车场拍摄，再经剪辑加入机场镜头<ref name="AUTOREF34">{{cite web | last = Malcolm | first = Shawna | date = 2007-10-15 | title = Exclusive First Look at ''Lost'' | work = ''TV Guide'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121112144651/http://bp1.blogger.com/_RrObyQ3XzcY/RxOJeZ8rK-I/AAAAAAAAKYY/HSZbsRUGoDQ/s1600-h/scan00020tk2.jpg | archivedate = 2012-11-12 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-11-12 | url = http://bp1.blogger.com/_RrObyQ3XzcY/RxOJeZ8rK-I/AAAAAAAAKYY/HSZbsRUGoDQ/s1600-h/scan00020tk2.jpg | format = JPG}}</ref>。虽然做了这么多的保密工作，但节目上映1个多星期前，互联网上就出现了详细而完整的剧情介绍<ref name="AUTOREF35">{{cite web | author = Lachonis, Jon | date = 2007-05-20 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-when-spoilers-attack-6709.aspx | title = LOST - When Spoilers Attack! | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150713063045/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-when-spoilers-attack-6709.aspx | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2015年7月13日 | publisher = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-02 }}</ref>，[[沃尔特·迪斯尼公司|沃尔特·迪斯尼公司]]对此展开调查<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | title = Ask Ausiello – Does ABC know how the rattlesnake leaked? | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-05-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021172857/http://www.tvguide.com/news/does-abc-know-30727.aspx | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/does-abc-know-30727/ | archivedate = 2012-10-21}}</ref><ref name="AUTOREF36">{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-05-30 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/curse-michael-ausiello-31334/ | title = Curse you, Michael Ausiello! ... | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | archivedate = 2014-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316135421/http://www.tvguide.com/news/curse-michael-ausiello-31334.aspx | deadurl = no}}</ref>。这起泄密事件也导致林道夫和库斯开始进入“[[无线电静默|无线电静默]]”状态，只在2007年[[圣迭戈国际动漫展|圣迭戈国际动漫展]]期间暂时取消<ref name="AUTOREF37">{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon | date = 2007-05-31 | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402135552/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-producers-comment-on-spoi-7045.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-producers-comment-on-spoi-7045.aspx | title = ''Lost'' Producers Comment on Spoiler-Gate '07 and ''Lost'' Season Four | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。剧末杰克前去参加追悼会的殡仪馆名叫“霍夫斯/道拉”（{{lang|en|Hoffs/Drawlar}}），其英语原文是“未来-{}-闪影”（{{lang|en|flashforward}}）一词的变位词<ref name="AUTOREF38">{{cite web | last = Hines | first = Ree | date = 2007-06-04 | url = http://www.today.com/id/18831266 | title = Months of Water-Cooler Talk in Wake of ''Lost'' | work = TODAY.com | publisher = NBCNEWS.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140513183300/http://www.today.com/id/18831266 | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-13}}</ref>。《迷失》主创人林道夫和[[J·J·艾布斯|J·J·艾布斯]]在节目构思期间就设想了“未来闪-{}-影”的情节设计<ref name="kristin">{{cite web | last = Veitch | first = Kristin | date = 2007-05-23 | title = Damon Lindelof Breaks 'Radio Silence' to Reveal Why Charlie Died and More | publisher = ''E!'' | accessdate = 2008-06-30 | archivedate = 2008-06-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080630083706/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=9c9aafc1-e118-4d0c-9686-6b982fbd4e87 | url = http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=9c9aafc1-e118-4d0c-9686-6b982fbd4e87}}</ref>，但库斯和林道夫是在第1季进入尾声时才开始进一步充实这一设想，因为他们这时已经意识到，倒叙式闪回的新鲜度终将耗尽，那时剧情就不得不切换为未来-{}-闪影<ref name="AUTOREF39">{{cite web | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | date = 2007-07-26 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070802.mp3 | title = ''Lost'' Season 4 Panel | work = ''Comic-Con International'' | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = yes | format = MP3 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185948/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070802.mp3 | archivedate = 2012-02-10}}</ref>。此外，根据美国广播公司发布的新闻稿，《迷失》将在《透过窥镜》48集后完结<ref name="AUTOREF40">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2007-05-07 | accessdate = 2014-09-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140922022609/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050707_01 | deadurl = yes | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050707_01 | title = ''Lost'' to Conclude in 2009–10 Television Season |  archivedate = 2014-09-22}}</ref>，所以剧组也很乐意从第3季终时就开始采用未-{}-来闪影<ref name="AUTOREF39" />。

本集的后期制作直到2007年5月21日才收尾，距节目在电视上首播只剩两天<ref name="podcast" />。配乐仍然由为《迷失》作曲的音乐家[[迈克·吉亚奇诺|迈克·吉亚奇诺]]谱写，并且本集中同样采用了多段流行音乐<ref name="AUTOREF41">{{cite web | date = 2007-11-11 | url = http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=recaps#t=38132&d=40701 | title = 05/23/2007 - "Through the Looking Glass"Season 3, Episode 322 | publisher = ''ABC'' | accessdate = 2009-06-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090616043235/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=recaps#t=38132&d=40701 | archivedate = 2009-06-16}}</ref>。查理在剧中演唱的歌曲正是由扮演者莫纳罕创作<ref name="AUTOREF42">Met/Hodder, "Through the Looking Glass" (enhanced).  Aired on 2007-01-30.</ref>。与之前两季的季终集一样，《透过窥镜》的长度也相当于其它剧集的两倍，为此，节目在[[加拿大|部分]][[巴西|国家]]播出时是分成上下两集，之后发行的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}也是如此<ref name="AUTOREF43">{{cite video | title = Lost: Terceira Temporada Completa – Explore Esta Aventura | date = 2007-09-25 | publisher = Buena Vista Home Entertainment | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.gringoscds.com.br/produtos/8640/lost--terceira-temporada-completa-explore-esta-aventura--7-disco- | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150904154812/http://www.gringoscds.com.br/produtos/8640/lost--terceira-temporada-completa-explore-esta-aventura--7-disco- | archivedate = 2015-09-04 | access-date = 2015-09-04 }}</ref>。与其它大部分《迷失》剧集不同的是，本集开场时没有“前情提要……”部分回顾之前的剧情发展，但根据原本的安排，节目开头会以《[[迷失剧集列表|迷失：答案]]》为题展示一段剪辑镜头，简要回顾第3季的剧情<ref name="AUTOREF44">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2007-05-07 | archivedate = 2012-02-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217154902/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050707_11 | deadurl = yes | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050707_11 | title = ''Lost'' Special Entertainment Press Release |  accessdate = 2012-02-17}}</ref>。据库斯表示，他和林德夫都觉得这集“非常酷，我们都为之感到自豪”<ref name="podcast" />。美国广播公司娱乐部总裁斯蒂芬·麦克弗森（{{lang|en|Stephen McPherson}}）称《透过窥镜》是《迷失》“最优秀的其中一集”<ref name="AUTOREF45">{{cite web | last = Veitch | first = Kristin | date = 2007-05-15 | url = http://www.eonline.com/print/index.jsp?uuid=5cd626fa-9bce-4563-8837-334f8a60d782&contentType=watchWithKristin | title = Watch with Kristin – ABC Berry Blast: Breaking Updates from Inside Lincoln Center | publisher = ''E!'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110629123441/http://www.eonline.com/print/index.jsp?uuid=5cd626fa-9bce-4563-8837-334f8a60d782&contentType=watchWithKristin | accessdate = 2011-06-29 | archivedate = 2011-06-29 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[博伟|博伟家庭娱乐]]于2007年12月11日发行《迷失》第3季的[[DVD区域码|1区]]{{lang|en|DVD}}和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光影碟]]套装，其中都收录了《透过窥镜》<ref name="AUTOREF46">{{cite web | author = Snugglefish Media | date = 2007-08-31 | publisher = Internet Brands | title = Disney Reveals New Specs, Exclusive Extras for 'Lost: Third Season' Blu-ray | work = ''High-Def Digest'' | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | archivedate = 2015-09-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150904161953/http://www.highdefdigest.com/news/show/Disney/TV_on_High-Def/Disney_Reveals_New_Specs_Exclusive_Extras_for_Lost_Third_Season_Blu-ray_/917 | url = http://www.highdefdigest.com/news/show/Disney/TV_on_High-Def/Disney_Reveals_New_Specs_Exclusive_Extras_for_Lost_Third_Season_Blu-ray_/917}}</ref>。以《迷失：地点》（{{lang|en|''Lost'': On Location}}）为名发行的制作特辑中收录了剧组和演员谈论几集节目制作的内容，《透过窥镜》就是其中一集。2008年1月30日，本集首度重播，荧幕下方三分之一的部分会显示一些文字，效果类似于{{lang|en|[[VH1|VH1]]}}电视网的[[弹出式视频|弹出式视频]]<ref name="AUTOREF47">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2008-01-24 | accessdate = 2012-02-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217154908/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=012408_05 | deadurl = yes | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=012408_05 | title = ABC Premieres a Special Enhanced Version of the ''Lost'' Season Three Two-Hour Finale | archivedate = 2012-02-17}}</ref>。受[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]的影响，这些弹出的文字不是由《迷失》的编剧创作，而是由行销公司米特/霍德（{{lang|en|Met/Hodder}}）提供<ref name="AUTOREF48">{{cite web|last=Carter |first=Bill |date=2008-01-30 |archivedate=2009-04-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423212826/http://www.nytimes.com/glogin?URI=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2008%2F01%2F30%2Farts%2Ftelevision%2F30lost.html&OQ=_rQ3D1Q26exQ3D1202360400Q26enQ3D5763e6487d948fddQ26eiQ3D5070Q26emcQ3Deta1&OP=67a2466eQ2F%29Q5DmQ2F%29I%2CGq-%2C%2C%215%295Q51Q51k%29Q513%29Q23Q51%29Q5B-%21q%29%21mXmvZqZ%2CD%29Q23Q51X%2Cq%21BY%21gX |deadurl=yes |title=Tropical Teaser: ''Lost'' Clues Decoded |work=''[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]'' |accessdate=2009-04-23 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/glogin?URI=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/30/arts/television/30lost.html&OQ=_rQ3D1Q26exQ3D1202360400Q26enQ3D5763e6487d948fddQ26eiQ3D5070Q26emcQ3Deta1&OP=67a2466eQ2F)Q5DmQ2F)I,Gq-,,!5)5Q51Q51k)Q513)Q23Q51)Q5B-!q)!mXmvZqZ,D)Q23Q51X,q!BY!gX }}</ref>。这一重播“增强版”一共吸引了近900万美国观众收看<ref name="AUTOREF49">{{cite web | last = Mitovich | first = Matt Webb | date = 2008-01-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316084834/http://www.tvguide.com/news/ratings-lost-repeat-14999.aspx | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/ratings-lost-repeat-14999/ | title = Ratings: ''Lost'' Repeat Has Some 'Pop' | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-03-16}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==

=== 收视率 ===
《透过窥镜》于2007年5月23日通过美国广播公司首播，长达两小时的播出时间里平均有1386万美国观众收看，在这周美国播映的所有电视剧里排名第4<ref name="AUTOREF51">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2007-05-30 | title = Weekly I. T. R. S. Primetime Program Ranking Report Entertainment Press Release | accessdate = 2014-11-29 | archivedate = 2014-11-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129013613/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=053007_07 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=053007_07}}</ref>，虽然这一成绩还没有达到第3季平均每集1460万的美国观众人数<ref name="AUTOREF52">{{cite news | work = ''Hollywood Reporter'' | date = 2007-05-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150726102550/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2006-07-primetime-wrap-137223 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2006-07-primetime-wrap-137223 | title = Series Programming Results 2006–07 Primetime Wrap | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2015-07-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但已明显比之前14集都要高<ref name="AUTOREF50">{{cite web | author = Nielsen Media Research | date = 2007-06 | archivedate = 2008-06-07 | url = http://www.yauws.com/content.php?id=7 | title = ABC's ''Lost'' Ratings at a Glance | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930150027/http://www.yauws.com/content.php?id=7 | work = ''Yet Another Useless Website'' | accessdate = 2008-06-07}}</ref>。节目前1小时的平均观众人数约为1267万，到第2小时则增至1504万<ref name="AUTOREF50" />。剧集在18至49岁年龄段观众群中取得的收视率为5.9/15，这意味着全美所有该年龄段人群里有5.9%观看节目首播，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群中则有15%选择收看《透过窥镜》<ref name="ratings">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2007-05-30 | archivedate = 2012-02-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217154621/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=053007_06 | deadurl = yes | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=053007_06 | title = Weekly Entertainment Primetime Ratings Wrap-Up Report Press Release | accessdate = 2012-02-17}}</ref>。节目在[[英国|英国]]首播时吸收了121万观众，是这周该国所有非地面电视台播出节目的收视亚军，仅次于《[[凯蒂和彼得：新篇章|凯蒂和彼得：新篇章]]》（{{lang|en|''Katie & Peter: The Next Chapter''}}）<ref name="AUTOREF53">{{cite web | author = Marcus | date = 2007-06-07 | url = http://gallifreyone.com/news-archives.php?id=6-2007#newsitemEElEkEEVkpQpiXmQsm | title = Human Nature – Final Ratings | work = ''Outpost Gallifrey'' | accessdate = 2009-05-23 | archivedate = 2009-05-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090523083448/http://www.gallifreyone.com/news-archives.php?id=6-2007#newsitemEElEkEEVkpQpiXmQsm | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]有117万观众收看本集首播，在这周所有电视节目里排名第51位<ref name="AUTOREF54">{{cite web | last = Dale | first = David | title = Stay in Touch – The Ratings Race: Big Brother's Big Night | publisher = ''The Sydney Morning Herald'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | date = 2007-07-31 | archivedate = 2012-05-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120504225227/http://blogs.smh.com.au/sit/archives/2007/07/the_ratings_race_consolations.html | url = http://blogs.smh.com.au/sit/archives/2007/07/the_ratings_race_consolations.html }}</ref>。《透过窥镜》在[[加拿大|加拿大]]首播时，前半集有91万1000观众收看，排名第16；后半集则有93万8000观众，排在第15位。节目的播出时段与《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》完全重叠，只是后者的时间更长，从《透过窥镜》播出前就已开始，电视剧播放完时仍未结束<ref name="AUTOREF55">{{cite web | work = ''BBM Canada'' | date = 2007-05-27 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05212007.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327012910/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05212007.pdf | title = Top Programs – Total Canada (English) | accessdate = 2009-03-27 | archivedate = 2009-03-27 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
