《透过窥镜》播出后获得评论界的普遍好评，多份评论中还认为这是《迷失》中最优秀的剧集之一<ref name="AUTOREF56">{{cite web | last = Shafrir | first = Doree | accessdate = 2015-09-04 | date = 2007-05-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150225132811/http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/summary_judgment/2007/05/losts_leap.html | url = http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/summary_judgment/2007/05/losts_leap.html | work = ''Slate'' | title =  ''Lost''<nowiki>'</nowiki>s Leap: The Critical Buzz on the ''Lost'' Season Finale | archivedate = 2015-02-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》称，本集节目不比寻常，“动感十足而又如同春季大清洗般令一堆人物死于非命”<ref name="AUTOREF57">{{cite news | last = Lloyd | first = Robert | date = 2007-05-24 | accessdate = 2010-02-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100209024627/http://lost-media.com/modules.php?name=News&file=article&sid=2554 | url = http://lost-media.com/modules.php?name=News&file=article&sid=2554 | title = ''Lost'' Finale: More Mysteries Wrapped in Enigmas | newspaper = ''Los Angeles Times'' | archivedate = 2010-02-09 | deadurl = yes | via = Lost-Media.com}}</ref>。《[[亚特兰大宪法报|亚特兰大宪法报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Atlanta Journal-Constitution''}}）表示，节目令人非常满意，虽然前1小时的开局略显缓慢，但第2小时可谓峰回路转，有许多让人高兴和难过的动人瞬间<ref name="AUTOREF58">{{cite web | last = Ho | first = Rodney | date = 2007-05-23 | title = Channel Serf – ''Lost'' Recap: Charlie, Hurley Save the Day | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208033514/http://www.accessatlanta.com/entertainment/content/shared-blogs/accessatlanta/tv/entries/2007/05/23/lost_in_the_moment.html | work = ''Access Atlanta'' | accessdate = 2012-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.accessatlanta.com/entertainment/content/shared-blogs/accessatlanta/tv/entries/2007/05/23/lost_in_the_moment.html | archivedate = 2012-02-08}}</ref>。[[美联社|美联社]]则认为，观众最初对《迷失》上瘾就是因为其精巧的构思和复杂的机关，这表现抢眼的季终集又一次做到了这点<ref name="AUTOREF59">{{cite news | last = Moore | first = Frazier | date = 2007-05-23 | deadurl = no | title = Gripping ''Lost'' Season-Ender Offers Hope | agency = ''[[美联社|Associated Press]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411173822/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/05/24/gripping-lost-season-ender-offers-hope/ | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/05/24/gripping-lost-season-ender-offers-hope.html | archivedate = 2015-04-11}}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》称赞本集不但节奏明快，扣人心弦的同时也回答了许多疑问，而且编剧们也做了一场引人注目的豪赌，告诉观众将来会发生什么，或许《迷失》在岛上的所有人都成功获救，他们实现了这一愿望。但很显然，从剧集中的向导人物杰克身上看来，编剧们无疑是在警告：“对自己的愿望也要保持警惕。”<ref name="AUTOREF60">{{cite news | last = Goodman | first = Tim | date = 2007-05-24 | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402100408/http://blog.sfgate.com/tgoodman/2007/05/24/lost-season-finale-no-one-gets-out-of-here-alive/ | url = http://blog.sfgate.com/tgoodman/2007/05/24/lost-season-finale-no-one-gets-out-of-here-alive/ | title = 'The Bastard Machine' – ''Lost'' Season Finale: No One Gets Out of Here Alive | newspaper = ''[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]]'' | deadurl = no}}</ref>《[[圣荷西信使报|圣荷西信使报]]》认为，《透过窥镜》在讲故事方面已经优异到令人瞠目结舌的程度<ref name="AUTOREF61">{{cite news | last = McCollum | first = Charlie | date = 2007-12-31 | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | url = http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_7850755?nclick_check=1 | title = TV's Top 25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905033411/http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_7850755?nclick_check=1 | archivedate = 2015-09-05 | newspaper = ''[[圣荷西信使报|San Jose Mercury News]]''}}</ref>。《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette''}}）评价，剧中的未来闪影扭转了这段传奇故事的势头，开始朝2010年的大结局迈进<ref name="AUTOREF62">{{cite news | last = Owen | first = Rob | date = 2007-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150407230803/http://www.post-gazette.com/tv/2007/12/27/Best-of-2007-Best-TV-Show-Mad-Men/stories/200712270255 | title = Best of 2007 – Best TV Show: ''Mad Men'' | newspaper = ''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette'' | url = http://www.post-gazette.com/tv/2007/12/27/Best-of-2007-Best-TV-Show-Mad-Men/stories/200712270255 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2015-04-07}}</ref>。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》在概括季终集的内容指出，本集剧情在两小时中突飞猛进，其中既有堆积成山的死尸，又有获得救援的可能，既有重大的虚假信息，也有对英雄主义的不同刻画，评论中还认为查理的死是《迷失》已经播出的剧集中最感人的桥段<ref name="AUTOREF63">{{cite news | last = Gilbert | first = Matthew | date = 2007-05-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150501214634/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2007/05/24/lost_finale_leaves_heads_spinning_in_a_new_direction/ | title = ''Lost'' Finale Leaves Heads Spinning in a New Direction | archivedate = 2015-05-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2007/05/24/lost_finale_leaves_heads_spinning_in_a_new_direction/ | newspaper = ''The Boston Globe'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05}}</ref>。《[[棕榈滩邮报|棕榈滩邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Palm Beach Post''}}）<ref name="AUTOREF64">{{cite news | last = Thompson | first = Kevin D. | date = 2007-12-21 | archivedate = 2015-04-03 | url = http://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/From-geeks-to-the-mob-it-was-a-year-to-remember-1590735.php | title = Wrapping Up 2007: Television | newspaper = ''The Palm Beach Post'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150403122633/http://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/From-geeks-to-the-mob-it-was-a-year-to-remember-1590735.php }}</ref>和《[[向导_(杂志)|向导]]》（{{lang|en|''Wizard''}}）都认为《透过窥镜》是2007年最扣人心弦的剧集<ref name="AUTOREF65">{{cite news | last = Morse | first = Ben | date = 2006-12-01 | url = http://lostmediamentions.blogspot.com/2007/12/wizard-names-lost-best-show-and.html | title = Wizard Names LOST Best Show and Cliffhanger of 2007 | work = ''Wizard'' | via = Dark UFO | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141231083107/http://lostmediamentions.blogspot.com/2007/12/wizard-names-lost-best-show-and.html | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-12-31}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》称赞节目有绝佳的节奏和动作场面，是成绩斐然的作品，但评论中认为其中的未来闪影无趣而拙劣<ref name="AUTOREF66">{{cite news | last = Ryan | first = Maureen | date = 2007-05-24 | title = ''Lost'' with Dr. House, er, I Mean Jack | archivedate = 2015-07-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150721221902/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2007/05/lost_with_dr_ho.html | newspaper = ''[[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2007/05/lost_with_dr_ho.html}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》将本集评为2007年最佳剧集<ref name="AUTOREF67">{{cite news | last = Poniewozik | first = James | date = 2007-12-20 | url = http://entertainment.time.com/2007/12/20/robopost_the_10_best_episodes/ | title = Robo-Post: The 10 Best Episodes of 2007 | work = ''Time'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402194358/http://entertainment.time.com/2007/12/20/robopost_the_10_best_episodes/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>，还认为其中“邮箱里的响尾蛇”是2007年所有电视节目中最出众的十佳片段之一<ref name="AUTOREF68">{{cite news | last = Poniewozik | first = James | work = ''Time'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402171434/http://entertainment.time.com/2007/12/21/robopost_the_10_best_tv_scenes/ | date = 2007-12-21 | url = http://entertainment.time.com/2007/12/21/robopost_the_10_best_tv_scenes/ | title = Robo-Post: The 10 Best TV Scenes of 2007 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-04-02}}</ref>。

“蒲团评论家”（{{lang|en|The Futon Critic}}）在评选年度50集最佳电视剧时，把《透过窥镜》排在首位<ref name="AUTOREF69">{{cite web |last=Sullivan |first=Brian Ford |accessdate=2015-09-05 |date=2008-01-11 |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/reviews/2008/01/11/the-50-best-episodes-of-2007-number-10-1-26422/20080111_bestof2007/ |title=The 50 Best Episodes of 2007: #10-1 |work=''The Futon Critic'' |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150905140130/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/reviews/2008/01/11/the-50-best-episodes-of-2007-number-10-1-26422/20080111_bestof2007/ |deadurl=no |archivedate=2015-09-05 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[E!|E!]]}}频道认为本集可能是整部《迷失》中的最佳剧集<ref name="kristin" />。《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》则称《透过窥镜》仿佛“一场令人目眩的运动历险，（观众）一直处在紧张的气氛中，构思精巧、制作精良，无论导演、表演还是制作都堪称极致”<ref name="roush">{{cite web | last = Roush | first = Matt | date = 2007-05-24 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/roush/way-end-season-10005.aspx | title = Roush Dispatch – Way to End a Season (Lost, Not Idol) | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2014-03-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316081626/http://www.tvguide.com/roush/way-end-season-10005.aspx | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}给予本集10分的最高评分<ref name="AUTOREF70">{{cite web | last = Van Horn | first = Jason | date = 2007-05-25 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/25/idiot-box-the-lost-season-3-finale | title = Idiot Box: The ''Lost'' Season 3 Finale | publisher = ''IGN'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2012-05-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120515225535/http://tv.ign.com/articles/791/791926p1.html}}</ref>，这也是该网站对《迷失》第3季剧集的最高评分，评论中称，《透过窥镜》无疑是以优异节奏完成故事讲述的大师之作<ref name="ign">{{cite web | last = Carabott | publisher = ''IGN'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | first = Chris | date = 2007-05-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140925121035/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/24/lost-through-the-looking-glass-parts-1-2-review | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/24/lost-through-the-looking-glass-parts-1-2-review | title = ''Lost'': "Through the Looking Glass, Parts 1 & 2" Review | archivedate = 2014-09-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。该网站还认为，节目中的未来闪影是2007年电视上最令人震惊的桥段<ref name="AUTOREF71">{{cite web | author = ''IGN'' staff | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131007221852/http://bestof.ign.com/2007/tv/10.html | deadurl = yes | date = 2007-12 | url = http://bestof.ign.com/2007/tv/10.html | title = Best of 2007: Biggest Shock – The Flashforward Reveal in ''Lost'' | publisher = ''IGN'' | accessdate = 2013-10-07 | archivedate = 2013-10-07}}</ref>。{{lang|en|IGN}}和《洛杉矶时报》之后都认为《透过窥镜》是《迷失》第2优秀的剧集，仅次于《[[常量_(迷失)|常量]]》（{{lang|en|''The Constant''}}）<ref name="AUTOREF">{{cite web|title=Ranking Lost |date=2010-06-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020192700/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/09/22/ranking-lost |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/09/22/ranking-lost |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-09-05 |archivedate=2014-10-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = 'Lost' 10s: Every episode of 'Lost,' ever (well, except the finale), ranked for your enjoyment | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2010-05-23 | first = Todd | last = VanDerWerff | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150228112418/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2010/05/lost-10s-every-episode-of-lost-ever-well-except-the-finale-ranked-for-your-enjoyment.html | archivedate = 2015-02-28 | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2010/05/lost-10s-every-episode-of-lost-ever-well-except-the-finale-ranked-for-your-enjoyment.html}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站称赞节目剧情难以预料的一面，称其它节目就是想要也根本做不到这点<ref name="dahl" />，该网站之后还在另一篇评论中认为本集是2007年最优秀的季终集<ref name="AUTOREF72">{{cite web | last = Williams | first = Don | date = 2007-12-24 | work = ''BuddyTV'' | title = Best Finale #1 | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120314013148/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/top-7-of-07-best-finale-1-lost-14961.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/top-7-of-07-best-finale-1-lost-14961.aspx | archivedate = 2012年3月14日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，而且查理的死也是2007年电视上最让人哀伤的死亡<ref name="AUTOREF73">{{cite web | last = Williams | first = Don | date = 2007-12-24 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/top-7-of-07-saddest-death-1-ch-15000.aspx | title = Saddest Death #1 | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2012年3月14日 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120314013159/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/top-7-of-07-saddest-death-1-ch-15000.aspx }}</ref>。此外，《透过窥镜》还是2007年{{lang|en|[[TV.com|TV.com]]}}网站评选的2007年度最佳电视剧集和“编辑推荐”剧集<ref name="AUTOREF74">{{cite web | work = ''TV.com'' | date = 2008-01-25 | archivedate = 2008-07-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080724222555/http://www.tv.com/special_feature/best-of-2007/episode/index.html | url = http://www.tv.com/special_feature/best-of-2007/episode/index.html? | title = The Best of 2007 – Best Episode | accessdate = 2008-07-24}}</ref>。《[[美国在线|美国在线]]》电视小队给予本集的评分为最高的7分，称“编剧们遵从德斯蒙德的预感，成功交出一份万众瞻目并且改变游戏规则的答卷”<ref name="AUTOREF75">{{cite web | last = Martell | first = Erin | date = 2007-05-23 | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2007/05/23/lost-through-the-looking-glass-season-finale | title = ''Lost'': 'Through the Looking Glass' (Season Finale) | work = ''AOL TV Squad'' | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521151313/http://www.tvsquad.com/2007/05/23/lost-through-the-looking-glass-season-finale/ | archivedate = 2011-05-21}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[TWoP|TWoP]]}}网站给予季终集的评级为最高级“{{lang|en|A}}”<ref name="AUTOREF76">{{cite web | last = Bates | first = Lulu | date = 2007-05-29 | url = http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/portal/site/TelevisionWithoutPity/menuitem.5853592f3d9209d415fc0f1045001d30/?strSeason=all&strSortCoulmn=grade_asc&ShowName=Lost&channelid=cb52b829275b2110VgnVCM1000006dc1d240____&hotfourmchannelid=3072b829275b2110VgnVCM1000006dc1d240____&pollchannelid=8562b829275b2110VgnVCM1000006dc1d240____ | title = ''Lost'' Full Episode Recaps | work = ''Television Without Pity'' | archivedate = 2007-07-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070929121201/http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/portal/site/TelevisionWithoutPity/menuitem.5853592f3d9209d415fc0f1045001d30/?strSeason=all&strSortCoulmn=grade_asc&ShowName=Lost&channelid=cb52b829275b2110VgnVCM1000006dc1d240____&hotfourmchannelid=3072b829275b2110VgnVCM1000006dc1d240____&pollchannelid=8562b829275b2110VgnVCM1000006dc1d240____ | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《[[悉尼晨锋报|悉尼晨锋报]]》认为，《透过镜像》中的未来闪影可能令《迷失》摆脱了剧集品质下滑的阴影<ref name="AUTOREF77">{{cite news | last = Dale | first = David | date = 2007-07-31 | title = Stay in Touch –The Tribal Mind: Just One Look, That's All It Took | newspaper = ''The Sydney Morning Herald'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140910203255/http://blogs.smh.com.au/sit/archives/2007/07/if_you_went_into_showing.html | url = http://blogs.smh.com.au/sit/archives/2007/07/if_you_went_into_showing.html | archivedate = 2014-09-10 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》评选2007年十佳电视剧集，本集榜上有名<ref name="AUTOREF78">{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819155009/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20165911_20165913_20167040%2C00.html |last=Snierson |first=Dan |title=The Best TV Episodes of 2007 |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-08-19 |date=2007-12-18 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20165911_20165913_20167040,00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-08-19 }}</ref>，评论中认为片尾未来闪影留下的悬念让观众意识到《迷失》创造的这个世界还会有新的维度<ref name="ew">{{cite web|last=Jensen |title=TV Watch: ''Lost'' – The Looking Glass War |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-11-29 |first=Jeff |date=2007-05-24 |archivedate=2014-11-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129233326/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20040061%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20040061,00.html }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Zap2It}}网站认为，部分观众可能对季终集可能会像之前一样大失所望，更多观众会感到非常迷茫，或是对剧集统筹无与伦比的心智惊叹不已<ref name="AUTOREF79">{{cite web | last = Porter | first = Rick | date = 2007-05-23 | url = http://zap2it.com/2007/05/finalewatch-lost-messes-with-our-heads-again/ | archivedate = 2014-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316084541/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2007/05/finalewatch-lost-messes-with-our-heads-again.html | title = Finalewatch: 'Lost' messes with our heads again | work = ''Zap2It'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。约翰·洛克一角在本集中的剧情反响不佳，{{lang|en|IGN}}网站的评论中认为，洛克从背后刺杀纳奥米，而且没有对自己的行径给出任何解释，这看上去很不合情理<ref name="AUTOREF80">{{cite web | last = Haque | first = Ahsan | date = 2007-05-25 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/25/idiot-box-the-lost-season-3-finale | title = Idiot Box: The ''Lost'' Season 3 Finale | publisher = ''IGN'' | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archivedate = 2012-05-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120515225535/http://tv.ign.com/articles/791/791926p1.html}}</ref>。林道夫对此表示，考虑到洛克之前遭到欺骗、枪击，还在达摩计划的乱葬岗躺了两天，他采取的任何行动都有一定的合理性，甚至能够更好地凸显人物个性<ref name="AUTOREF81">{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819163734/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20151394%2C200.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20151394,200.html |title=Burning Question of the Month |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-08-19 |archivedate=2014-08-19 }}</ref>。电影、电视导演兼编剧[[凯文·史密斯|凯文·史密斯]]表示，制作《迷失》第3季，并且突然抛出弧线球，这实在太有戏剧性，也太让人满足了，让人只想对着编剧们摘下帽子……然后来个大大的击掌拥抱<ref name="AUTOREF82">{{cite web|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-10-09 |archivedate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006213338/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20151394%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20151394,00.html |title=Kevin Smith Raves About ''Lost'' |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</re